1. *Billy* je prošao svoju ispitnu godinu u školi sa odličnim rezultatima. (*Billy* passed his exam year in school with excellent results.)

2. Devojka se zaljubila u *Billyja* i nije mogla da se otarasi njegovog utiska. (The girl fell in love with *Billy* and couldn't shake off his impression.)

3. *Billyjev* prijatelj je bio vrlo zabrinut za njegovo zdravlje. (*Billy's* friend was very concerned about his health.)

4. Učitelj je otkrio *Billyja* kako se krije u uglu učionice. (The teacher found *Billy* hiding in the corner of the classroom.)

5. *Billyje* roditelji su mu dali punu podršku u svemu što je pokušavao da postigne. (*Billy's* parents gave him full support in everything he tried to achieve.)